{"tid":1363453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[接力] 點解RTHK被陰乾 - 2","createTime":"2019-07-25T07:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T12:09:33.000Z","uid":184643,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0685e4977b2d1c83793e54dc4d4149e1cdaa33","tid":1363453,"uid":184643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:39:18.000Z","msg":"我幫個朋友出po 嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cVveMYK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcVveMYK.png&h=5a464570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多謝同事之前個po 《<strong>點解RTHK被陰乾<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359867\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359867</a></strong>》，我想補充少少<br />\n<br />\n亞視不獲續牌，港台<strong>2016年4月</strong>開始<span style=\"color: red;\">接亞視頻道</span>，令所需嘅播放時數大增，由2015年嘅17,029.4 升至2016年35,593.8，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兩倍有多</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但係預算就只係加<span style=\"color: red;\">23%</span> 至5.13億。局方面就成日砌詞話，俾港台嘅資源年年都加，但就算去到2018年，播放時數36,163 (比2015年 <span style=\"color: red;\">+112%</span>)，而預算只係 <span style=\"color: red;\">+35%</span>。<strong>根．本．就．唔．夠</strong>﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個<span style=\"color: green;\">筆直咁tight</span>，所以好多同事絞盡腦汁點樣節省成本。喺哩個情況之下，重新<span style=\"color: green;\">包裝舊節目</span>同<span style=\"color: green;\">《漫．電視》</span>應運而生。唔好笑啊，哩樣嘢唔係港台獨有。2009年，挪威國家廣播電視台 NRK 就整咗個慶祝「卑爾根線」 100 週年既<span style=\"color: green;\">七個鐘長節目</span>，仲好受歡迎好高收視。之後其他國家包括澳洲SBS、比利時、英國BBC、紐西蘭、法國、西班牙都<span style=\"color: green;\">有同類節目</span>。聽同事講，《漫．電視》有一啲篇章係啲同事去旅行搭火車set 個cam，甚至喺屋企砌模型set 個cam咁樣拍成嘅，夠<span style=\"color: green;\">低成本</span>喇掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但係另一邊廂議員<span style=\"color: red;\">盧偉國</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔識野又唔理來龍去脈</span>就喺立法會<span style=\"color: red;\">笑港台《漫．電視》<strong>播龜</strong></span>﹗點解要有《漫．電視》？咪就係你哩啲建制派，不斷話港台大白象<span style=\"color: red;\">唔肯批錢落嚟</span>囉﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講起大白象，港台當年建<span style=\"color: green;\">新大樓</span>就俾各大傳媒/立法會建制派圍插，話<span style=\"color: red;\">大花筒</span>。我哋又睇下數字。<br />\n2014年港台新大樓預算造價<strong>60億</strong><br />\n2019年批出<span style=\"color: red;\">入境處新總部<strong>68億</strong></span><br />\n2019年批出<span style=\"color: red;\">數碼港第五期<strong>55億</strong></span><br />\n可以見到其實唔係差好多。港台嘅大樓設計<span style=\"color: green;\">唔係淨係辦公室</span>，仲要有大大小小嘅<span style=\"color: green;\">廠/錄音或直播室</span>，廠有廠嘅setting，由佈景、樓底嘅燈光設置、機器等等，哩啲都會需要額外嘅錢。所以當年真係主要係<span style=\"color: red;\">輸咗俾輿論</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n講真，你估同事好想搬去將軍澳？根本而家廣播道幾棟大樓<span style=\"color: red;\">舊到不能</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最近<span style=\"color: red;\">男廁仲漏屎水</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。而且節目多左，就算請到人做，<span style=\"color: red;\">office都唔夠位坐</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！文職果啲早幾年已經被逼搬左去旺角，嚟緊連製作嘅部門都要搬去觀塘咁遠，來來回回嘥幾多時間！如果唔係環境咁惡劣，真係冇人會想搬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHard-sell 一下先，其實港台嘅製作真係好好睇，最近反送中嘅大家有眼睇，除此之外仲想推介一集鏗鏘集︰<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">《八九演義》第三回﹕尋</span> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wuL_QurTJrE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwuL_QurTJrE&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=8217c671\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wuL_QurTJrE</a>，跟拍「天安門母親」發言人走訪六四死難家屬，紀錄佢哋點樣連公開悼念子女都唔敢。<br />\n仲有<span style=\"color: green;\">《三中商》</span> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q7Od4uDt61U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQ7Od4uDt61U&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=75cbc39f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q7Od4uDt61U</a>，直接追住中聯辦問嘢(7&rsquo;19&rdquo;)，真係好值得欣賞。<span style=\"color: green;\">請大家多多支持港台呀﹗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人﹗加油﹗</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有frd 子話佢會長開港台(<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=287db62e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv</a>)以作支持。或者大家喺街上見到港台記者，都可以打聲招呼呀，<span style=\"color: green;\">港台哥哥/ 港台姐姐</span>都好靚仔靚女架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾位港台員工<br />\n<br />\n附註︰聯合國教育、科學及文化組織認為公共廣播(public broadcast)服務是：<br />\n由公眾製作、資助和監控的廣播服務，並以服務公眾為目的。公共廣播服務並非商營或國營的廣播服務，不受政治干預和商業力量所影響。透過公共廣播服務，公民可獲得資訊、教育和娛樂。如能保障意見多樣化、節目多元化、編輯自主、有適當資金、具有問責性和透明度，則<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">公共廣播服務可作為民主的基石</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"d505042dad2d18dfee9970e8a9fb947aaf332864","tid":1363453,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57ccc3aaa05351c7611e7906bf1e0f9afb42908","tid":1363453,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddff9f8a268a6b6132aecf0387679cc46d1723e","tid":1363453,"uid":289558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:44:30.000Z","msg":"睇31真係有營養好多<br />\n五夜講場真係唔錯，尤其是文學放得開。好想藝術同火速救兵都好睇。之前有D外購節目同音樂會都好正！<br />\n<br />\n港台加油啊！尤其是記者，辛苦了！<img sr