;\">盧偉國</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔識野又唔理來龍去脈</span>就喺立法會<span style=\"color: red;\">笑港台《漫．電視》<strong>播龜</strong></span>﹗點解要有《漫．電視》？咪就係你哩啲建制派，不斷話港台大白象<span style=\"color: red;\">唔肯批錢落嚟</span>囉﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講起大白象，港台當年建<span style=\"color: green;\">新大樓</span>就俾各大傳媒/立法會建制派圍插，話<span style=\"color: red;\">大花筒</span>。我哋又睇下數字。<br />\n2014年港台新大樓預算造價<strong>60億</strong><br />\n2019年批出<span style=\"color: red;\">入境處新總部<strong>68億</strong></span><br />\n2019年批出<span style=\"color: red;\">數碼港第五期<strong>55億</strong></span><br />\n可以見到其實唔係差好多。港台嘅大樓設計<span style=\"color: green;\">唔係淨係辦公室</span>，仲要有大大小小嘅<span style=\"color: green;\">廠/錄音或直播室</span>，廠有廠嘅setting，由佈景、樓底嘅燈光設置、機器等等，哩啲都會需要額外嘅錢。所以當年真係主要係<span style=\"color: red;\">輸咗俾輿論</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n講真，你估同事好想搬去將軍澳？根本而家廣播道幾棟大樓<span style=\"color: red;\">舊到不能</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最近<span style=\"color: red;\">男廁仲漏屎水</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。而且節目多左，就算請到人做，<span style=\"color: red;\">office都唔夠位坐</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！文職果啲早幾年已經被逼搬左去旺角，嚟緊連製作嘅部門都要搬去觀塘咁遠，來來回回嘥幾多時間！如果唔係環境咁惡劣，真係冇人會想搬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHard-sell 一下先，其實港台嘅製作真係好好睇，最近反送中嘅大家有眼睇，除此之外仲想推介一集鏗鏘集︰<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">《八九演義》第三回﹕尋</span> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wuL_QurTJrE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwuL_QurTJrE&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=8217c671\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wuL_QurTJrE</a>，跟拍「天安門母親」發言人走訪六四死難家屬，紀錄佢哋點樣連公開悼念子女都唔敢。<br />\n仲有<span style=\"color: green;\">《三中商》</span> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q7Od4uDt61U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQ7Od4uDt61U&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=75cbc39f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q7Od4uDt61U</a>，直接追住中聯辦問嘢(7&rsquo;19&rdquo;)，真係好值得欣賞。<span style=\"color: green;\">請大家多多支持港台呀﹗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人﹗加油﹗</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有frd 子話佢會長開港台(<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=287db62e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv</a>)以作支持。或者大家喺街上見到港台記者，都可以打聲招呼呀，<span style=\"color: green;\">港台哥哥/ 港台姐姐</span>都好靚仔靚女架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾位港台員工<br />\n<br />\n附註︰聯合國教育、科學及文化組織認為公共廣播(public broadcast)服務是：<br />\n由公眾製作、資助和監控的廣播服務，並以服務公眾為目的。公共廣播服務並非商營或國營的廣播服務，不受政治干預和商業力量所影響。透過公共廣播服務，公民可獲得資訊、教育和娛樂。如能保障意見多樣化、節目多元化、編輯自主、有適當資金、具有問責性和透明度，則<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">公共廣播服務可作為民主的基石</span></strong>。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:49:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6070646d54465045767857e37e5b79d0db175f3","tid":1363453,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:49:30.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe7e8302226e507cbf2ab428f194bab11bb5897","tid":1363453,"uid":84575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:04:54.000Z","msg":"睇過一集《漫．電視》講木工既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心好睇過CCTVB同時段既9唔搭既節目，<del>可以笑下個師傅做得差</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然希望你地可以有多ｄ筆直整套Doctor Who級數既劇，撐你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c63754480d3ff0e50c404569a6ae5d7f268493","tid":1363453,"uid":281129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"支持 港台節目<br />\n有意思得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6211ce7ada5344bff7cf77e1310a32e3d241aef","tid":1363453,"uid":217757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:45:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac2ff0185bd174255c3da4414ad52ea2b7f73132","tid":1363453,"uid":54719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:09:33.000Z","msg":"港台真係衰在無budget<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但喺依個budget下做到咁既野真係超哂水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}